# ========= 数据目录（绝对不进 Git）=========
backend/mysql/data/
backend/redis/data/
backend/proxysql/data/

# ========= 真实密码文件（不进 Git，只有 .env.example 进入）=========
**/.env

# ========= SQL 备份文件 =========
backend/mysql/*.sql
backend/mysql/*.sql.gz

# ========= SSL 证书 =========
nginx/certs/
**/*.pem
**/*.key

# ========= 系统文件 =========
.DS_Store
*.log
.cursorignore
monitor/mysqld-exporter.cnf

# Local secret staging for Ansible migration
secrets-staging/

bj-01-configs/
gz-01-configs/
gz-02-configs/

# ========= Obsidian 工作区配置 =========
Docs/.obsidian/

# ========= Ansible vault 密码文件 =========
vault/.vault-pass

# ========= 个人学习规划 =========
# 整个 Docs/scheme/ 目录默认不进 Git（求职策略备忘录、复盘清单等私密内容）
# 仅 phase-1 架构演进路线图作为面试可见的工程素养证据，单文件白名单
# 注意：必须用 Docs/scheme/* 而非 Docs/scheme/，否则目录级忽略会压制文件级 negation
Docs/scheme/*
!Docs/scheme/phase-1-architecture-upgrade.md